Abstract = {{Accurate experimental values for the vibrational ground tone or
   fundamental vibrational energy splitting of H-2, HD, and D-2 are
   presented. Absolute accuracies of 2 x 10(-4) cm(-1) are obtained from
   Doppler-free laser spectroscopy applied in a collisionless environment.
   The vibrational splitting frequencies are derived from the combination
   difference between separate electronic excitations from the X-1
   Sigma(+)(g), v = 0, J and v = 1, J vibrational states to a common EF1
